Here's a UI from which we
removed all the images and text.

13
00:00:41,480 --> 00:00:43,340
What do you think this app does?

14
00:00:43,340 --> 00:00:45,070
There may be more than
one correct answers,

15
00:00:45,070 --> 00:00:46,780
so don't think about it too hard.
